CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 29, 1963, pg. 19, reads: "1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama Exhibitors who were not shown on last week's picture page are shown here...Niagara Cyclo Massage: Charles Murphy, John Gogul, Art Lund, George Townsend, Isabel Powell, Agnes Moore, Dorothy Rutherford, Leo Lash, Vio Fogel, Mary Lash... All Home-A-Rama Photos (Including last week's) by Charles (Teenie) Harris."
TitMainTitle: Niagara Cyclo-Massage booth with men and women, including Charles Murphy, John Gogul, Art Lund, George Townsend, Isabel Powell, Agnes Moore, Dorothy Rutherford, Leo Lash, Vio Fogel, and Mary Lash giving demonstrations to visitors, at 1963 Pittsburgh Courier - WAMO, Home-A-Rama fair, Syria Mosque
